data.description: 'ROSEMONT EA'  The Rosemont is a beautiful and spacious two-story home! On the first floor you will find a large bedroom suite with a walk-in closet with access to unique under-stairwell storage. The first floor also has a comfortable family area, utility room, full guest bath, and a second bedroom. The second floor has three additional bedrooms, a shared game room, and one full bathroom. Smart home features are also included for added convenience.
